  dialogeLines:
  - whoSayes: DOCTOR
    whatSayes: Well. That's unusual.
  - whoSayes: DOCTOR
    whatSayes: 'So the rumors were true.

'
  - whoSayes: DOCTOR
    whatSayes: God's little lamb descending into Hell.
  - whoSayes: DOCTOR
    whatSayes: Haha... isn't that funny? Hahahahahaha... Hahahahahahahahaha.. haha..
      ha...
  - whoSayes: DOCTOR
    whatSayes: Ha...
  - whoSayes: player
    whatSayes: ...
  - whoSayes: DOCTOR
    whatSayes: You shouldn't be here, player.
  - whoSayes: DOCTOR
    whatSayes: 'Which makes you <b>interesting</b>.

'
  - whoSayes: DOCTOR
    whatSayes: 'And <b>interesting</b> things deserve examination.

'
  - whoSayes: DOCTOR
    whatSayes: Let's see what <i>your beloved God</i> put inside you.
